<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Heart-blood" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Heart-blood,</orth> 1) blood shed in death, lifeblood: <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.172" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 172</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.2.131" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 4.28.131" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.3.83" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 3, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 2.2.66" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B II, 2, 66</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.223" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 223</bibl>.<lb />2) the soul, the essence: <cit><quote>the mortal Venus, the h. of beauty,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 1, 34</bibl></cit>.
